@startuml
title Activity Diagram: Customer Journey - Check Ferry Safety
skinparam ConditionEndStyle hline
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor White
skinparam ActivityBorderColor DarkGreen
skinparam ArrowColor DarkGreen

|#Honeydew|Customer|
start
:Open Ferrycast App / Website;
:View **Home/Landing Page**;

if (Knows Route?) then (Yes)
    :Enter **Origin** & **Destination**;
    :Select **Travel Date**;
    :Click "Search Ferries";
else (No, Browsing)
    :Browse **Popular Routes**;
endif

|#LightBlue|Frontend (Vue.js)|
:Request Route Options;

|#LightGray|Backend (Laravel)|
:Fetch Available Schedules;
:Calculate **Current Safety Score** for each;
note right
  Quick Pass:
  Green (Safe)
  Amber (Caution)
  Red (High Risk)
end note

|Frontend (Vue.js)|
:Display List of Ferries;
:Show **Safety Badges** next to times;

|Customer|
:Select a specific Trip;

|#LightBlue|Frontend (Vue.js)|
:Request Detailed Forecast;

|#LightGray|Backend (Laravel)|
:Fetch Detailed Wind/Wave Model;
:Generate **Navigation Advice**;

|Frontend (Vue.js)|
:Show **Forecast Dashboard**;
note right
  - Hourly Weather
  - Wave Height Graph
  - Cancellation Probability
end note

|Customer|
:Review Safety Analysis;
if (Risk is High?) then (Yes)
    :Check Alternative Dates;
    :Or **Subscribe to Alerts** (FCM);
else (No, Safe)
    :Proceed to Booking / Plan Trip;
endif

stop

@enduml
